Source: https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/training/modules/interact-with-data-blazor-web-apps/

dotnet commands:
  - Create new project using blazorserver template: dotnet new blazorserver -o ProjectName -f net6.0
  - Create new razor component: dotnet new razorcomponent -n ComponentName -o Pages
  - Create new gitignore: dotnet new gitignore